    "We further conduct a family-engaged user evaluation to assess the effectiveness of our APP in facilitating communication.",
    "The feedback proves quite positive, with users expressing a high level of satisfaction and an increase in the frequency of Auslan use, underscoring the positive impact of our efforts.",
    "Background and related work Isolated sign language recognitionIsolated Sign Language Recognition (ISLR) is one of the primary tasks in sign language processing, which involves classifying individual signs in a video to corresponding glosses.",
    "In an ISLR model, the extraction of features is of paramount importance.",
    "Contemporary ISLR research [6,[8][9][10] predominantly employs CNN-based structures, such as I3D [11] and S3D [12]."
